snippet.title: Johnny Depp OFFICIALLY REHIRED | Back In a New Pirates of the Caribbean 6 Movie?
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp is OFFICIALLY REHIRED for a New Pirates of the Caribbean 6 Movie!

The case between Amber Heard and Johnny Depp is one that everyone is talking about right now. As time goes on and the anticipation builds while fans of the actors wait for the official court hearing, Amber Heard is starting to loose her credibility and put herself in a pretty bad situation, one that will be hard to come back from. She is even rumored to go to prison for false accusations! After Johnny Depp starting to prove his innocence, he is starting to get back his career, which he might get in Pirates of the Caribbean 6! 

If you enjoyed this video and would like to see more similar animated satirical content in the future make sure to like and subscribe!
